<span id="freeTextContainer212799108918981924">My goto Italian cookbook. This is the essence of Italian cooking simple recipes using great ingredients. The recipes are simple and logical. Italian does not have to have garlic and gravy like sauce to be Italian. <br/><br/>American&apos;s often learned what Italian food was from emigrants from the south Italy that opened restaurants using red checkered table clothes. These neighborhood eatery&apos;s of the 60&apos;s and 70&apos;s often used too much garlic and served food of poor quality in my opinion. <br/><br/>Hazan will broaden yo</span>
  <span id="freeText212799108918981924" style="display:none">My goto Italian cookbook. This is the essence of Italian cooking simple recipes using great ingredients. The recipes are simple and logical. Italian does not have to have garlic and gravy like sauce to be Italian. <br /><br />American's often learned what Italian food was from emigrants from the south Italy that opened restaurants using red checkered table clothes. These neighborhood eatery's of the 60's and 70's often used too much garlic and served food of poor quality in my opinion. <br /><br />Hazan will broaden your horizons and ground you in food the way you will find in in Italy. True Italian is at the heart of slow cooking and farm to fork.</span>
